  <description type="morphology">dichasial; &lt;bracts not linear-subulate&gt;. Flowers 3–5 mm diam.; sepals usually lanceolate to narrowly oblong, rarely oblanceolate, equal, 2.5–2.5 × 0.8–1 mm, &lt;margins sometimes ciliate, not setulose-ciliate&gt;, apex rounded; petals pale yellow, oblong, 1.7–3.5 mm; stamens 5–16, scarcely grouped; styles 0.5 mm; stigmas broadly capitate. Capsules narrowly ovoid to cylindric-ellipsoid, 4–5 × 2–2.5 mm, &lt;usually broadest at or near middle&gt;. Seeds 0.4–0.7 mm; testa finely linear-scalariform. 2n = 16 [“18”].</description>
